channel.title: [Utopia] Highly Edited Clean/Blank Delta
channel.description:
[center][img]http://img703.imageshack.us/img703/821/94473689.png[/img]
[shadow=red,left][size=36pt][b]Release: Utopia Clean/Blank Version[/b][/size][/shadow]
[b]I decided to release my base of my current development Utopia. If you are sick of PI's (with already everything in it or loading 600+ shit, or in general) or you want to start up your server from zero with a clean base. Then this server is for you :D[/b][/center]
[size=18pt][b]Information:[/b][/size]
[size=16pt][b]Server:[/b][/size] [b]- Every single class has been re-organized. - 75% of the content has been retabbed for conventions, to get rid of the horrible look of people adding stuff via notepad and don't tab. - Every single class has been controlled on unnused or unneeded code, and removed those. Most should be out. - Many improvements all-round have been done. - Fully packaged[/b]
[size=16pt][b]Game:[/b][/size] [b]- Practically everything from clicking objects to skills and minigames have been removed. - Rewritten prayer - Partly redone combat - Basic NPC clipping[/b]
[size=16pt][b]Still Contains:[/b][/size] [b]- Global Drops - Combat System - Quest templates - Drinking potions, eating food (redone cleaner & better) - Small content of npc's (hitting, prayers ect..) - Skill Guides - Base files for some content. - Pickables - Basic commands - Burying bones - Equipment required levels[/b]
[size=18pt][b]Some media:[/b][/size]
[IMG]http://img685.imageshack.us/img685/2487/23226668.png[/img]
[IMG]http://img862.imageshack.us/img862/5677/68003626.png[/img]
[IMG]http://img841.imageshack.us/img841/600/84969327.png[/img]
[IMG]http://img696.imageshack.us/img696/8748/73557920.png[/img]
[IMG]http://img820.imageshack.us/img820/6550/19912292.png[/img]
[i]Package Explorer:[/i] http://img835.imageshack.us/img835/6645/555t.png
[size=18pt][b]Credits:[/b][/size] - Spades for the absolute base - Delta - Me - Lostmyphat for some help on the way
[size=18pt][b]Download:[/b][/size] [b]Server download:[/b] http://up.ht/HLOzzG [b]Client download (iskape):[/b] http://up.ht/HLP6Sb [b]Package:[/b] http://up.ht/HLP8JO
[size=18pt][b]Note:[/b][/size] Without my permission you are NOT allowed to (re)release this server anywhere.
